// VALIDATION (after import — expect these ranges)
// ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
// Portfolio view (all 6 EU + TR buildings):
//   Building Avg Headcount Business Hours  → 300–500  (weighted avg)
//   Building Peak Headcount                → 800–1200 (Healthcare/Edu peak)
//
// Per building (business hours avg ≈ max_occupants × ~0.6):
//   B001 Berlin Office       (260 max)   →  ~150
//   B002 Istanbul Retail     (700 max)   →  ~400
//   B003 Hamburg Logistics   ( 80 max)   →   ~45
//   B004 Vienna Hotel        (230 max)   →  ~140
//   B005 Frankfurt Healthcare(750 max)   →  ~450
//   B006 Amsterdam Edu       (950 max)   →  ~570
//
// These ranges match base-archetype occupancy profiles
// (EN 15232 typical business-hours fill rate).
// ════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
